  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0ba8\u0bca\u0b9a\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd 82 \u0baa\u0bcb\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b95\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bcd \u0b92\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A person was arrested with 82 bottles of kasip in Kilinochchi",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Kilinochchi Police have informed that a person has been arrested with 82 bottles of kasip in Kilinochchi.",
        "The arrest was made in the Dharmapuram area under Kilinochchi Dharmapuram Police Division on the night of 24th yesterday.",
        "During the search conducted based on the secret information received by the army, 82 bottles of liquor and 238 liters of coda were also recovered, and a suspect was arrested by the army and later handed over to the Dharampuram police station on the charge of possessing equipment used for the production of liquor and a domestic gun.",
        "The Darumapura police are conducting further investigations into the incident and have informed that steps have been taken to produce the person in court today."
      ],
